{
  "stem": "22469.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The same, the same.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We've been all three in Jewish Zionist organization.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Akiba, or [HEBREW]",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Please?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were together almost every evening to learn Hebrew, and and another of Zionists, and [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not religious, not religious.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just Zionist.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Akiba, we've been just young people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I-- when I was-- I was 18, I went to older people, or the organization [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we start already to smoke cigars, and dancing, and flirting, and--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is-- yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Eve.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Melnek.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They killed her in the war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1940.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Cracow, because we should leave Cracow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She went with her parents to a one village outside Cracow, and we went with my parents to another village.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we didn't see each other anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had been forced to leave.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just as people stay in ghetto, or they get permission from the German.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the German pick up these people what was necessary for them to make the arms of the industry.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in ghetto after.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After, when they concentrate-- this was '42.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They concentrate people in Cracow ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And from Cracow ghetto, they sent groups of thousands of thousands of people to gas chamber like Belzec, or Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did not answer that question.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When Hitler came here?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Immediately.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From my friend, Polish, very good friend, we start to be little bit distance.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I blame maybe the Polish church, and the rest German propaganda.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because the Polish church, they were always anti-semite.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No curfew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the war?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No curfew, no, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nothing, nothing.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Official, we had the same right, The Jews, the same right like the Polish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But unofficial, they boycott us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "For example, if somebody from Jewish people wanted to study medicine, is well not possible.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
